  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <div type="mūlam" rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNV1">
      <l>akattatum puṟattatu māyiru pakutiyiṉ</l>
<l>mikuttatu māki virintatu poruḷē</l></lg>
<p xml:lang="en"><hi rend="italic">Poruḷ</hi> is expanded into that which is <hi rend="italic">akam</hi>,
that which is <hi rend="italic">puṟam</hi> and that which exceeds those two categories.</p>
</div>
</body>
</text>
<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <head xml:lang="en">Commentary</head>
<p xml:id="TNV1comm1">eṉpatu, niṟutta muṟaiyāṉē poruḷilakkaṇam āmāṟuṇarttutaṉutaliṟṟu. eṉavē yivvōttup poruḷiyal eṉpatāyiṟṟu.</p>
<p xml:id="TNV1comm2">(itaṉ poruḷ.) akattiṉ ākiya vakapporuḷum, puṟattiṉ ākiya
puṟapporuḷum, āyiru vakaiyiṉum ākiya akappuṟapporuḷum eṉa mūvīṟṟatāyp pal vēṟu
vakaippaṭṭa tuṟaikaḷāṟ parappuṭaiyatu poruḷāmeṉṟavāṟu. </p>
<p xml:id="TNV1comm3">puṟac ceykai uḷateṉiṉum mikutivakaiyāl akampaṟṟi nikaḻtaliṉ
irutalaiyum tīrā vaṉpiṟṟākiya kāmam akapporuḷ eṉpatu. akanikaḻcci uḷateṉiṉum
mikuti vakaiyāṟ puṟacceykaiyāl nikaḻtaliṟ kuṟṟappāṭillā maṟam puṟapporuḷ eṉpatu.
akamallā iṉpamum puṟamallāp poruḷ ceyal vakaiyum aṟamum ataṉ payaṉākiya vīṭum
iruvakai nikaḻcciyum nōkkik kōṭaliṉ akappuṟapporuḷ eṉappaṭṭaṉa veṉpatu. (1)</p>

 
 </body>
 </text>     
